channel.title: Command to make 'fake players.'
channel.description:
I know 'fake players' don't act like real players, or send the same amount of packets, but i want to test how much my server can hold,
So could someone tell me how to do this& answer this Question, okay lets say i have 50k 'Fake Players' how many real players would that be equivalent to?
